x-2=0
\ln x = 0
x=2
x=1
(x-2)\ln x=0\\  \longleftrightarrow x-2=0 \text{ or } \ln x=0 \\ \longleftrightarrow x=2 \text{ or } x=1
\text{If }\textit{ab}=0
\Rightarrow\textit{a = 0}\quad or\quad b = 0
(\text{You should know this in elementary school})
(x-2)\ln{x}=0
\Rightarrow\text{(x - 2)}=0\quad or\quad \ln{x}=0
